title: Mariah Carey - Obsessed [PROMO 2009] New Single
description:
Mariah Carey - Obsessed [PROMO 2009] New Single

Mariah Carey released Obsessed on June 15 as the lead impact single off her upcoming album Memoirs of an Imperfect Angel. The song is produced and co-written by Mariah Carey, The-Dream and Christopher "Tricky" Stewart. And is under Island Records. The shooting of the music video is set to be on TBA. The single was released by Def Jam and promoted by Def Jam. Currently the song is only available on radio, but has been brought to you here, by yours truly.

The song has also been rumored to be targeted at rapper Eminem who reportedly dated Mariah a few years back. Mariah herself has not responded to these rumors. 

A remix of this song was released on the same day.
